## Steps

1. Words + to lower case
2. Formula to remove vowels from shortcuts + to lower case
3. Add quotations for the words and replacements
4. Add the trigger and replace 
5. Format so when you drag down it automatically fills in with the trigger, replace
6. Add propagate_case and word : true true
7. Add formual with $cell$ to make sure they always fill correctly
8. Finally copy paste to the part that fixes the spacing for number propagate_case and word


